<h3 align=center>U.S. Department of Health and Human Services Public Health Service, June 1994</h3>
<h2 align=center>Child Health Guide</h2>
<h3 align=center>PUT PREVENTION INTO PRACTICE</h3>
<p><strong>Important Information</strong></p>
