<a href="#depressants">DEPRESSANTS</a> | <a href="#hallucinogens">HALLUCINOGENS</a> | <a href="#narcotics">NARCOTICS</a> | <a href="#designer">DESIGNER DRUGS</a> | <a href="#anabolic">ANABOLIC STEROIDS</a></li>
</ul>
</li>
