Press, P.O. Box 20190, Cathedral Finance Station, New York, NY 10025. $2.95. A 40-page activity book for children in 
grades 1-4 that contains pictures of the damage that marijuana does to the body. Whiskers Says No to Drugs, 1987. Weekly 
Reader Skills Books, Field Publications, 245 Long Hill Road, Middletown, CT 06457. $1.50. This book contains stories and 
follow-up activities for students in grades 2 and 3 to provide information and form attitudes before they face peer pressure to 
experiment.</p>
<h4>GENERAL READING LIST FOR SECONDARY SCHOOL CHILDREN</h4>
