<p><a href="../index.html#toxic"><img src="../article/../workers.gif" alt=" [Workers Injured By Toxics] " align=bottom border=0 width=142 height=33></a> <a href="../article/lenses.shtml"><img src="../lenses.gif" alt=" [Bausch &amp; Lomb Contact Lenses Class Action] " align=bottom border=0 width=142 height=33></a> <a href="http://seamless.com/alexanderlaw/nccc/cb-intro.html"><img src="../sm-nccc.gif" alt=" [National Consumer Complaint Center] " align=bottom border=0 width=142 height=33></a> <a href="../reserved.html"><img src="../reserved.gif" alt=" [Settlement Reached - GM Pickup Truck] " align=bottom border=0 width=142 height=33></a> 
