<head>
<title>Magazine Telephone Scams -- November 1992</title>
<meta name="GENERATOR" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
</head>

<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
<p><!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//IETF//DTD HTML//EN">

<html>

<head>
<title></title>
<meta name="GENERATOR" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
</head>

<body>
