<HTML>
<HEAD><TITLE>AACI - Message from the President</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BACKGROUND="bgrnd.jpg" BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#0000FF" VLINK="#800080" ALINK="#FF0000">
<IMG SRC="logo-sm.gif" WIDTH=394 HEIGHT=48><HR>
<UL>


<CENTER><FONT SIZE=+2>

<B><I>Message From<BR>AACI President Helaine Gerber and<BR>Executive Director Leah Ronen</I></B>
</FONT></CENTER>
<HR WIDTH=60% ALIGN=center>
<P>


Here we are, AACI, once again MAKING A DIFFERENCE.
Over the years, AACI has assisted tens of thousands of North American Olim in making their home in Israel. It has enabled many of these olim to make an impact on Israeli Society.It is AACI that initiated the legislation to stop smoking in public places in Israel and to assure health benefits for Senior Citizens from abroad. It is AACI that brought the concept of beginning in schools to educate about ecology and environment.  It is AACI that is currently leading the battle against reckless driving that is killing more Israelis than terror or war.
<P>
AACI can be active in all of these areas because AACI has brought the spirit of volunteerism to Israel.  Across the country, thousands of volunteers are active in a score of activities. Volunteers meet new olim at the airport.  Volunteers assist newcomers to settle in. Volunteers run programs to meet the needs of our consituency. Volunteers organize successful lobbying. AACI volunteers have taught the concept of volunteerism to native born Israelis. 
<P>
And now,in our ongoing effort to provide the most comprehensive service to our members and prospective olim, we invite you visit our Home Page, your first stop on the way home...to Israel.






</UL>
