<HEAD><TITLE>AACI - Travel Experience</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BACKGROUND="bgrnd.jpg" BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#0000FF" VLINK="#800080" ALINK="#FF0000">
<IMG SRC="logo-sm.gif" WIDTH=394 HEIGHT=48><HR>
<UL>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=+3><EM><STRONG>THE AACI TRAVEL EXPERIENCE<BR>OPERATED BY OPHIR TOURS</STRONG></EM></FONT></CENTER><HR WIDTH=60% ALIGN=center><P>
The AACI Travel Experience was created for you the AACI member. 
We have harnessed AACI's purchasing power to provide direct savings for 
AACI members and provide AACI with valuable income to help expand its 
services for all of us.<P>
The AACI Travel Experience is operated by us through Ophir Tours, 
which was selected for offering the maximum benefits to our members.<P>
The AACI Travel Experience is now in its fourth year and we have sold 
more than 8,000 airline tickets through the program since its inception, 
in addition to providing domestic tourism opportunities at a reduced cost.<P>
<DL>
<DT>For more details contact the Ophir Tours office nearest you. 
Ask for<dd><STRONG>THE AACI TRAVEL EXPERIENCE</STRONG><P>
</DL>
<DL>
<DT><STRONG>Jerusalem:</STRONG><dd>3 Shlomzion Hamalka St. Tel: 02-6240548, 02-6252777 Fax: 02-6240491<P>
<DT><STRONG>Central & Tel Aviv:</STRONG><dd>32 Ben Yehuda St. Tel Aviv Tel: 03-5269660  Fax: 03-5253377<P>
<DT><STRONG>Raanana:</STRONG><dd>141 Ahuza Tel: 09-7741125 Fax: 09-7741058<P>
<DT><STRONG>Sharon & Netanya:</STRONG><dd>15 Smilansky St. Netanya  Tel: 09-8615027, 09-8829564 Fax: 09-8615032<P>
<DT><STRONG>North & Haifa:</STRONG><dd>62 Ha'atzmaut St. Haifa  Tel: 04-8673011<P>
<DT><STRONG>BeerSheva:</STRONG><dd>132 Keren Kayemet St.  Tel: 07-6278515<P>
<DT><STRONG>Domestic Travel:</STRONG><dd>Debbie Sinai  32 Ben Yehuda St. Tel Aviv Tel: 03-5269797<P>
