<HTML>
<HEAD><TITLE>AACI - AACINSURANCE</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BACKGROUND="bgrnd.jpg" BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#0000FF" VLINK="#800080" ALINK="#FF0000">
<IMG SRC="logo-sm.gif" WIDTH=394 HEIGHT=48><HR>
<UL>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=+3><EM><STRONG>AACINSURANCE Ltd.</STRONG></EM></FONT></CENTER><HR WIDTH=60% ALIGN=center>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=+2><EM><STRONG>THE WHY? WHERE? WHAT? and HOW?</STRONG></EM></FONT></CENTER><P>
<FONT SIZE=+1>O</FONT>ne of the most difficult challenges of life in Israel is the Insurance industry. AACI members have been culturally challenged by the differences between the Israeli and the North American insurance industries.<P>
<UL TYPE=disc>
<LH><H3>Why AACINSURANCE Ltd.?</H3></LH><P>
<LI>Israeli insurance law and practice are different than in North America. 
Even if one were fluent in Hebrew, the policies are hard to understand.<P>
<LI>The variety of insurance policies that are standard in North 
America were not available in Israel.<P>
<LI>The small size of the insurance base, as compared to much larger 
populations in Canada and the USA, means that there is a constant 
fluctuation in the price of policies. Preferential treatment is 
given to special groups.<P>
<LI>The "WAR ZONE" clause increases the cost of many policies.<P>
</UL>
AACI took control by establishing our own agency to cater to the 
"critical requirements" of North American Olim.<P>
<STRONG>Where did AACI get the idea to develop its own Insurance 
Agency?</STRONG><P>
The idea to develop such an agency came right out of our North American 
Heritage.<P>
It is common practice in North America for non-profit organizations 
like AACI to develop their own insurance programs to meet the needs of 
their membership. Bnei Brith, AARP (American Association of Retired People) 
are  two examples of organizations offering large insurance programs 
of this type. Like these organizations the profits from AACINSURANCE Ltd. 
are directed to AACI to help increase services to you the member.<P>
<STRONG>What is AACINSURANCE Ltd.</STRONG><P>
AACINSURANCE Ltd. integrates all four essential insurance elements --- <BR>
The Agents, The Policies, The Collective, And The Claims Collection. 
The result is a symbol of quality insurance service for AACI members.<P>
The number one issue for AACI members is the basic need to TRUST their 
Insurance <STRONG>Agent</STRONG>. Agents are admitted to the 
AACINSURANCE Ltd. program only if they can prove themselves on these 4 
critical requirements;  <STRONG>Integrity, Professionalism, Client 
orientation and Communication.</STRONG><BR>
AACINSURANCE Ltd. agents are located all across Israel.<P>
AACI members wanted policies similar to the ones available in North 
America and tailored to their needs. AACINSURANCE Ltd. has developed, and 
is continuing to develop, the widest range of value-added policies, 
made specially for AACI members.<P>
A goal of AACINSURANCE Ltd. is to have all policies and other 
documents in English. Most documents are now in English and translation 
assistance is available at no extra cost.<P>
AACI stands behind you the member, in providing the easiest, most 
efficient and unique claims system in Israel. In cases of a problem 
AACI acts as your champion to protect your rights.<P>
AACINSURANCE Ltd. identified as a particular area of focus Marine 
Insurance and Claims handling in Israel.<P>
Marine or air cargo Insurance protects your household goods while 
they are on the move from your North American home  to the local port 
where your shipment will be assembled, across sea to the Israeli 
port, possibly to warehouse storage and ultimately to your new home in 
Israel. Each move is a multiplication of many opportunities for 
your goods to be damaged, lost or stolen. To the credit of the shipping 
industry, there is very little damage or theft compared to the 
volume of shipment and handling on the way.<BR>
<EM>AACI can't pack your personal belongings or accompany them 
safely to your home in Israel. We can provide you with "peace of mind" 
so if something does go wrong, you are well protected.</EM><P>
<STRONG>How do I contact AACINSURANCE Ltd.</STRONG><P>
For all your insurance needs be in touch Toll free in Israel with 
AACINSURANCE LTD. 177-022-5670, your local AACI regional office, and 
in the USA 1-800-922-2465.<P>
</UL>

