<HTML>
<HEAD><TITLE>AACI - Auto Insurance Guide</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BACKGROUND="bgrnd.jpg" BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#0000FF" VLINK="#800080" ALINK="#FF0000">
<IMG SRC="logo-sm.gif" WIDTH=394 HEIGHT=48><HR>
<UL>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=+3><EM><STRONG>Auto Insurance Guide</STRONG></EM></FONT></CENTER><HR WIDTH=60% ALIGN=center><P>
<DL>
<LH><H4>In Israel there are three types of car insurance:</H4></LH>
<DT><STRONG>Compulsory</STRONG> (biutach hova)<dd>Covers injuries 
to individuals.  This type of insurance is mandatory and a prerequisite 
for renewing the car's yearly registration.  The actual certification 
proving payment must remain in the car at  all times.  Compulsory 
insurance is paid for at a bank at the time of registration renewal.

<DT><STRONG>Third-party</STRONG> (bituach tzad shlishi)<dd>Covers 
property damage caused by the policyholder's car (but not the damage 
sustained by his or her car).  The insurance premium is paid to an 
insurance company.

<DT><STRONG>Comprehensive</STRONG> (bituach makif)<dd>Covers theft, 
fire and property damage in case of an accident to the policyholder's 
vehicle, as well as third-party insurance.  This insurance premium is 
also paid to an insurance company.
</DL><P>


<H4>DEDUCTIBLE</H4>
Most insurance policies include a provision requiring policyholders 
to pay for a portion of any damages to their car.  The size of the deductible is 
specified in the policy and is generally linked to the Consumer Price 
Index.  A claim paid by the insurance company to the policyholder is 
the amount remaining after subtracting the deductible.<P>
Speak with your closest <A HREF="insure.htm"> AACINSURANCE</A> Agent for 
more details
</UL>

<BOTTOMINSERT>
<CENTER>
<A HREF="http://www.jer1.co.il/cgi-bin/imagemap/aacimap"><IMG 
SRC="botmbutn.gif" border=0 ISMAP></A><P>

<center><font size=-2>
<A HREF="natnl.htm">National AACI</A> | <A HREF="aliyah.htm">Pre-Aliya Information </A> | 
<A HREF="jer.htm">Jerusalem Region </A> | <A HREF="netanya.htm">Netanya Region </A> | 
<A HREF="central.htm">Central Region </A> <br>
<A HREF="north.htm">Northern Region </A> | 
<A HREF="south.htm">Southern Region </A> | <A HREF="ben&serv.htm">Benefits & Services </A>
</font>
</center><P>

